---
title: "Dynamic: Load Report"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant DataSvc as AccessIntelligenceDataService
    participant PersistSvc as ReportPersistenceService
    participant EncryptSvc as AccessReportEncryptionService
    participant Server as Bitwarden Server
    participant UI as UI Components

    Note over Browser: Page load / org context initialized
    Browser->>DataSvc: initializeForOrganization$(orgId)
    DataSvc->>DataSvc: loadExistingReport$(orgId)
    Note over DataSvc: loading$ = true

    DataSvc->>PersistSvc: loadReport$(orgId)

    par Load from backends in parallel
        PersistSvc->>Server: getRiskInsightsReport$(orgId) — metadata
        PersistSvc->>Server: getRiskInsightsSummary$(orgId) — summary
        PersistSvc->>Server: downloadReport$(orgId) — encrypted payload (planned)
    end
    Server-->>PersistSvc: metadata + summary + encrypted payload

    PersistSvc->>EncryptSvc: decryptReport$(context, encryptedData, wrappedKey)
    Note over EncryptSvc: versioning services parse + validate payload
    EncryptSvc-->>PersistSvc: DecryptedAccessReportData

    PersistSvc->>PersistSvc: assemble AccessReportView from<br/>decrypted payload + metadata + summary

    PersistSvc-->>DataSvc: AccessReportView

    DataSvc-->>UI: report$ emits AccessReportView
    Note over UI: loading$ = false<br/>UI renders report
